snippet.title: Metal Slug Mobile 3 (Allen's Battle Chronicles) playthrough
snippet.description:
IT'S NOT OVER YET!
Click the Closed Captions button for crummy commentary.

Recorded in Kemulator, played with a Logitech USB Precision controller (pro-tip: delete the "jinput-dx8.dll" file for better compatibility with Joy2Key!)
